                "another movable carriage oriented at 55 degree with",
                "respect to the beam axis."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BGO"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The gamma-rays from the reaction to be studied",
                "were detected in BGO detection system.",
                "The BGO crystal is a cylinder (length = 28 cm) with a",
                "coaxial hole (diameter = 6 cm) and a radial thickness",
                "of 7 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 25Mg targets have been produced from enriched 25MgO",
                " (enrichment 99+-1%). The 25MgO was mixed with Ta",
                "powder, heated with an electron beam and evaporated on",
                "Ta backings, thickness 0.3 mm. The nominal 25Mg target",
                "density, approx. 65 mug/cm**2, corresponded to a 30 keV",
                "thickness at E(p)= 100 keV."
              ]
            }
